The badge component adds an indicator or counter on a child component

### Basic usage
```jsx
<Badge onMouseDown={function noRefCheck(){}}>
  <Button leftIcon={function noRefCheck(){}}>
    What's new
  </Button>
</Badge>
```

### As counter

```jsx
<Badge type="counter" count={100} maxDigits={2}>
    <Button leftIcon={WhatsNew}>{"What's new"}</Button>
</Badge>
```